s/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"large\">泰利 &middot; 路易威登主要事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></p><br />\n係舊登扮絕症，獲得一眾巴絲同情後就扮慘眾籌呃錢加呃蝦條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />舊登有紀錄但已經開唔返，以前line/ig都叫Terry2500，好多巴絲表示當年d人幾百一千咁捐比佢，自己追po睇返。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdtqxpB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdtqxpB.png&h=70b0526d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiLHvOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiLHvOQ.png&h=47e1b27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbz9aOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffbz9aOX.png&h=160440ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">舊登巴絲上水爆料</span><br />\n[/quote]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2348292/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2348292/page/1</a><br />\n#17開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwD9wcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwD9wcR.jpg&h=d6c58174&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wox2RcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwox2RcR.jpg&h=6ed3b84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母當年話自己每分每秒d骨都痛到好似比火燒咁 又話自己有玻璃骨 行路都會腳斷 生活好大負擔呃咗幾撚多巴絲金錢同時間上嘅慰藉<br />\n見係絲打就流曬口水 打電話嚟傾一陣就問人係咪處女 <br />\n又話自己因為病冇女 日日就呻冇女冇女冇女<br />\n叫人入屯門探你唔肯就屌鳩人 話人唔重視你 鳩痕就認啦<br />\n同你好撚熟咩仆街 又話就死 7年啦 死撚左去邊呀？還錢先啦<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">泰利公爵(身價1x-20萬)富豪生活曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></p><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i